      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA GOLD (2) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only one length (24.10) behind IT'S SNOWTIME at this track. Has good early burn and is drawn to be prominent. One of the contenders. DOZEN DONUTS (8) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (24.07) at this track in a Maiden over 407m. One of the prime contenders. SON OF MINYA (1) is still a maiden after nine runs but rarely far away, the latest filling a minor placing when third at Q Straight. Has finished in the money the last two starts. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expected to feature again. DARK END (4) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 2.5 lengths away in second (24.60). Well placed and gets his chance.",
